    old "She gasps. “Seriously? Just a moment!” She disappears behind the wall and soon after that, the gate is opened. While you dismount next to the wood splitting spot, a couple of people surround you, pointing at your mount and commenting on its appearance, though they step away whenever {color=#f6d6bd}[horsename]{/color} makes a rapid movement. \n\n{color=#f6d6bd}The guard in the yellow armor{/color} is the only one who steps forward. She raises her hands, as if to pet your palfrey, but doesn’t touch it. “It looked smaller from above,” she whispers loudly. “How do I even get up there?” "
